snippet.title: Freelife | Official Trailer | 202 Studio
snippet.description:
Freelife: A Canvas for Your Imagination | Steam Playtest Coming in early 2024!

Welcome to Freelife, a voxel-based landscape where your boundless creativity meets the bustling streets of a reimagined Golden Bay. This is more than just a game; it's an evolving platform for innovation, a realm of endless possibilities, and a testament to the courage of its inhabitants.

As you step into this world, your imprint will refine its very essence. Embark on a journey of co-creation and witness the world of Freelife grow through collective imagination.

Take the helm — mold Freelife into a monument of collective brilliance. Craft your saga.


Join the genesis. Leave your mark!
■ Discord: https://discord.gg/SqSNTAkuXX
■ Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/freelife202std
■ Twitter: https://twitter.com/freelife202std
■ Official Website : https://202stud.io/
